author: rbb
msg: Add the sendfile test to the testsock program.  This allows make test to
get all the way through the test suite and report if everything is
successful or not.  In order to do this, I had to rename the testsf.c
file to sendfile.c.  We can't name the program testsf, because the
find script would find it, and then we don't get through the test suite.
